full_text: This happens all over the place (see: Cochran, Thad). Not sure how we institute term limits or set a maximum age limit (imo it should be 70) at which point you can’t hold elected office anymore, but it needs to happen. https://t.co/TC8A33YCBd
Same governmental organization, same topic, two very different outcomes. If the CDC desires to continue eroding its credibility, it’s doing a phenomenal job. https://t.co/H9q1pxdzEo
